-- Altech Earnings in East Africa to Rise, Business Report Says
-- B y   A n d r e s   R .   M a r t i n e z
-- 2012-03-04T13:02:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-04/altech-earnings-in-east-africa-to-rise-business-report-says.html
Allied Technologies Ltd. (ALT)  may get
about a third of its earnings from eastern Africa as it expands
operations in the region, Business Report said.  The Johannesburg-based company operates about 6,200
kilometers (3,583 miles) of fiber optic cable in the region,
the newspaper said, citing Chief Executive Officer Craig Venter.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andres R. Martinez in Johannesburg at 
